<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="16e462db-e1d1-479e-b215-e33c23c0f0e3" >

    <h2>Next steps</h2> 
<p>Participants voiced their wish for a follow-up roundtable next year. Several suggestions were provided for possible topics at this second gathering:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Establishment of an association of equity officers.</li> 
 <li>Discussion of the “made in Canada” Athena SWAN (Scientific Women’s Academic Network) initiative being implemented by the federal government.</li> 
 <li>Updates on NSERC 2020, especially as this plan relates to NSERC’s Framework on Equity, Diversity and Inclusion.</li> 
 <li>Updates from other granting agencies and university equity offices on ongoing initiatives that could serve as EDI best practices.</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
